data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority35
ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadCsePerson
data.value: select T1.NUMB from CKT_CSE_PERSON T1 where exists ( select * from CKT_LEGAL_ACT_PERS T2 where T1.NUMB = T2.CSP_NUMBER and T2.ACCOUNT_TYPE = 'S' and @ladRNumber = T2.LAD_R_NUMBER and @lgaRIdentifier = T2.LGA_R_IDENTIFIER and T2.END_DT > @endDt )

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, PATERNITIES_EST from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = 'JD'

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, PATERNITIES_EST from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: ReadLegalActionLaDetNonfinancialFipsTribunal
data.value: select * from ( select T1.LEGAL_ACTION_ID, T1.CLASSIFICATION, T1.FILED_DT, T1.STANDARD_NO, T1.ESTABLISHMENT_CD, T1.TRB_ID, T2.LA_DETAIL_NO, T2.NON_FIN_OBLG_TYPE, T2.DETAIL_TYPE from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION T1 join CKT_LEGAL_ACT_DTL T2 on (T1.FILED_DT between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) and T1.STANDARD_NO > @standardNo and (T1.ESTABLISHMENT_CD in ('CS', 'CT')) and T1.CLASSIFICATION = 'J' and T1.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T2.LGA_IDENTIFIER and T2.NON_FIN_OBLG_TYPE = 'EP' and T2.DETAIL_TYPE = 'N' ) S1 cross apply ( select top(1) FIP_STATE, FIP_COUNTY, FIP_LOCATION, TRIBUNAL_NM, JUDICIAL_DISTRICT, IDENTIFIER from CKT_TRIBUNAL where IDENTIFIER = S1.TRB_ID and FIP_LOCATION is not null and FIP_COUNTY is not null and FIP_STATE is not null and FIP_COUNTY > 0 ) S2 order by S1.STANDARD_NO, S1.FILED_DT

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority35
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set AS_OF_DATE = @asOfDate, PATERNITIES_EST = @paternitiesEst where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId
